# Google Calendar "secret iCal" feed URL for pulling UFA event dates.
#
# Get it: Google Calendar (web) → hover your calendar in the left sidebar →
# ⋮ → Settings and sharing → "Integrate calendar" → copy the
# "Secret address in iCal format" (ends in /basic.ics).
#
# Only events whose title or description contains "[UFA]" or
# "Ultimate Fighting Agents" are published to the site.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste the URL. `.env.local` is gitignored,
# so it is never committed. For deploys, set the same value as a GitHub Actions
# secret named GCAL_ICS_URL.
GCAL_ICS_URL=
